<h2 id="section-top">Respiratory Medicine</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=1410">Royal Papworth Hospital NHS Foundation Trust</a>
</p>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="service-locations clear">
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address">Main Switchboard<br/>01480 830541</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent108753b8da4744069406c64883ebcb44">
</div>
<p>Our <a href="http://www.papworthhospital.nhs.uk/content_new.php?/our_services/preview_-_thoracic_services_lungs" target="_blank">Thoracic Services</a> Directorate provides care to patients with a wide range of acute and chronic chest conditions. This includes the interstitial lung disease service, the respiratory infection, inflammation and immunology service and surgery for lung cancer.</p>
<p>Papworth Hospital has established global renown as a clinical and research centre of excellence. We have 15 Chest physicians, 10 visiting chest physicians, two dedicated thoracic surgeons and one cardiothoracic surgeon. Our expert team includes radiologists, pathologists, nurses and physiotherapists, with additional input from dietetics, occupational therapy and psychological medicine. All of these teams have a special interest in diseases of the chest and collectively they offer specialist patient care.</p>
<p><strong>Please follow the relevant link for more information about specific services:</strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.papworthhospital.nhs.uk/ccli/cli_cystic_fibrosis.php" target="_blank">Cystic Fibrosis </a></strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.papworthhospital.nhs.uk/ccli/" target="_blank">The Cambridge Centre for Lung Infections</a></strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.papworthhospital.nhs.uk/content_new.php?/our_services/thoracic_services_lungs/interstitial_lung_disease" target="_blank">Interstitial Lung Disease</a></strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.papworthhospital.nhs.uk/content_new.php?/our_services/thoracic_services_lungs/pulmonary_vascular_disease_unit_pvdu" target="_blank">Pulmonary Vascular Disease</a></strong><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.papworthrssc.nhs.uk/" target="_blank">Respiratory Support and Sleep Centre</a></strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.papworthhospital.nhs.uk/content_new.php?/our_services/preview_-_thoracic_services_lungs/preview_-_thoracic_oncology" target="_blank">Thoracic Oncology (Lung Cancer)</a></strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.papworthhospital.nhs.uk/content_new.php?/our_services/preview_-_thoracic_services_lungs/preview_-_thoracic_surgery" target="_blank">Thoracic Surgery</a></strong></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong> </strong></p></div>
